{"tid":86752,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"今日同個朋友食譚仔。。。","createTime":"2017-01-19T09:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T13:54:08.000Z","uid":1657,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"38766d3c3cdce4f7bcf26cf66a382d6798699de2","tid":86752,"uid":1657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:57:14.000Z","msg":"佢同我講佢好食得辣<br />\n一坐低，嗌野食果陣。。<br />\n朋友：呀姐，要個炸醬雞肉 10小辣<br />\n我聽到果刻我好想笑 但我要忍住，想比番個面子佢<br />\n食完之後 <br />\n佢話：個辣真係一d味都冇囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我話：緊係啦 10小辣不嬲係唔辣<br />\n聽到之後 佢面都綠埋<br />\n作為佢朋友，我下次仲應唔應該同佢食譚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38f8ef19abc57f0b5a5c813b5d10bd237f3fa8d","tid":86752,"uid":39064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa131905c335823658a9760e571995681b9c1a2","tid":86752,"uid":9436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:02:59.000Z","msg":"應該 下次幫佢叫雙特辣"},{"pid":"bc8c8a93a32280f257d57f764171fb812403f492","tid":86752,"uid":56139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:09:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該 下次幫佢叫雙特辣</blockquote><br />\n雙特辣試過仲廢過麻辣特辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051258747c848f39b559fa89fe59b336bfc19d38","tid":86752,"uid":1657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該 下次幫佢叫雙特辣</blockquote><br />\n我怕佢下次嗌清湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd27df0fad970eb2eb5718c49ed4fb8bd2067ce9","tid":86752,"uid":16511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:20:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該 下次幫佢叫雙特辣</blockquote><br />\n雙特辣試過仲廢過麻辣特辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一蘭二百倍辣<img src=\"https://img.